Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.82,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}我这污秽的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.07,OP,,0,0,0,,{\1vc(&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&,&H838383&,&H838383&)}究竟会斩向何方
